---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-6">Quantum Computing for Network Engineers</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Entangled Packets bridges the gap between traditional networking expertise and quantum computing concepts. 
        Prepare for the future of networking with clear, accessible explanations tailored for networking professionals.
      </p>
      <a href="/articles" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-md transition-colors">
        Explore Articles
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 border-t border-neutral-200">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-8">Quantum Computing Fundamentals</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- These will be dynamically generated from content collection when we have articles -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-primary-700 mb-2">Quantum Bits (Qubits) and Superposition</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Understanding the fundamental unit of quantum information and how it differs from classical bits.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Read Article →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-primary-700 mb-2">Quantum Entanglement Explained</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Exploring the phenomenon of entanglement and its implications for quantum networking.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Read Article →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/articles" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">View All Articles →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-primary-50 -mx-4 md:-mx-6 px-4 md:px-6 border-y border-primary-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-6 text-center">Why Quantum Computing for Network Engineers?</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-10">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3.75v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 9M3.75 20.25v-4.5m0 4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 15M20.25 3.75h-4.5m4.5 0v4.5m0-4.5L15 9m5.25 11.25h-4.5m4.5 0v-4.5m0 4.5L15 15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary-700 mb-2">Future-Proof Career</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Stay ahead of the curve as quantum networking emerges as a new industry direction.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary-700 mb-2">Practical Relevance</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Learn quantum concepts with clear connections to networking principles you already understand.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-primary-700 mb-2">Cutting-Edge Security</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Understand quantum cryptography and its implications for network security protocols.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
